er/svg/1575fa23f185305b9707f6919b0d5359d8158a87" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -4.671ex; width:64.539ex; height:10.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {=
\begin{aligned}{\hat {\varepsilon }}_{i}&amp;=3Dy_{i}-{\hat {y}}_{i}=3Dy_{i=
}-({\hat {\alpha }}+{\hat {\beta }}x_{i})=3D{\text{residuals}}=3D{\text{est=
imated errors}},\\{\text{SSR}}&amp;=3D\sum _{i=3D1}^{n}{{\hat {\varepsilon =
}}_{i}}^{2}=3D{\text{sum of squares of residuals}}.\end{aligned}}}"></span>=
</dd></dl>
<p>Then <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>t</i></span><sub>score</sub> is given by
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e t_{\text{score}}=3D{\frac {({\hat {\beta }}-\beta _{0}){\sqrt {n-2}}}{\sq=
rt {\frac {SSR}{\sum _{i=3D1}^{n}(x_{i}-{\bar {x}})^{2}}}}}.}">
