          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mtext>score</mtext>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mi>r</mi>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <msqrt>
                  <mi>n</mi>
                  <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </msqrt>
              </mrow>
            </mrow>
            <msqrt>
              <mn>1</mn>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <msup>
                <mi>r</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
            </msqrt>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>,</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle t_{\text{scor=
e}}=3D{\frac {r{\sqrt {n-2}}}{\sqrt {1-r^{2}}}},}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/0b352cb2142064ce27ba30161b1faeb355021676" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -3.171ex; width:17.657ex; height:7.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle t_=
{\text{score}}=3D{\frac {r{\sqrt {n-2}}}{\sqrt {1-r^{2}}}},}"></span></dd><=
/dl>
<p>where <i>r</i> is the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pearson_c=
orrelation_coefficient" title=3D"Pearson correlation coefficient">Pearson c=
orrelation coefficient</a>.
</p><p>The <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>t</i></span><sub>score, intercept</su=
b> can be determined from the <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>t</i></span><sub>s=
core, slope</sub>:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e t_{\text{score,intercept}}=3D{\frac {\alpha }{\beta }}{\frac {t_{\text{sc=
ore,slope}}}{\sqrt {s_{\text{x}}^{2}+{\bar {x}}^{2}}}},}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
