{\bar {\Delta }})^{2}}"></span>
is not a pooled variance. For use in significance testing, the distribution=
 of the test statistic is approximated as an ordinary Student's <i>t</i>-di=
stribution with the degrees of freedom calculated using
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
