h the famous <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Behrens%E2%80%93Fishe=
r_problem" title=3D"Behrens=E2=80=93Fisher problem">Behrens=E2=80=93Fisher =
problem</a>, i.e., comparing the difference between the means of two normal=
ly distributed populations when the variances of the two populations are no=
t assumed to be equal, based on two independent samples.
</p><p>The test is developed as an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/Exact_test" title=3D"Exact test">exact test</a> that allows for <b>unequal=
