r {\mathbf {x} }}_{2}\right)'{\mathbf {S} _{\text{pooled}}}^{-1}\left({\bar=
 {\mathbf {x} }}_{1}-{\bar {\mathbf {x} }}_{2}\right).}"></span></dd></dl>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"The_two-sample_t-test_is_a_=
special_case_of_simple_linear_regression">The two-sample <i>t</i>-test is a=
 special case of simple linear regression</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection=
"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DStudent%27s_t-test&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D23" title=3D"Edit section: The two-sample t-test is a special case of=
 simple linear regression"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsecti=
on-bracket">]</span></span></div>
