sols.com/">https://www.statsols.com/</a>
</p><p><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external free" href=3D"https://support.=
sas.com/documentation/onlinedoc/stat/131/intropss.pdf">https://support.sas.=
com/documentation/onlinedoc/stat/131/intropss.pdf</a>
</p><p><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external free" href=3D"https://www.ibm.=
com/products/spss-statistics">https://www.ibm.com/products/spss-statistics<=
/a>
</p><p><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external free" href=3D"https://www.stat=
a.com/features/power-and-sample-size/">https://www.stata.com/features/power=
