</p><p><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external free" href=3D"https://support.=
minitab.com/en-us/minitab/help-and-how-to/statistics/power-and-sample-size/=
supporting-topics/power-and-sample-size-analyses-in-minitab/">https://suppo=
rt.minitab.com/en-us/minitab/help-and-how-to/statistics/power-and-sample-si=
