</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Software_implementations">S=
oftware implementations</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"m=
w-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.=
php?title=3DStudent%27s_t-test&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D25" title=3D=
"Edit section: Software implementations"><span>edit</span></a><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Many <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spreadsheet" title=3D"Spre=
adsheet">spreadsheet</a> programs and statistics packages, such as <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QtiPlot" title=3D"QtiPlot">QtiPlot</a>, <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LibreOffice_Calc" title=3D"LibreOff=
ice Calc">LibreOffice Calc</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mi=
crosoft_Excel" title=3D"Microsoft Excel">Microsoft Excel</a>, <a href=3D"ht=
tps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SAS_(software)" title=3D"SAS (software)">SAS</a=
>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SPSS" title=3D"SPSS">SPSS</a>, =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stata" title=3D"Stata">Stata</a>, =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DAP_(software)" title=3D"DAP (soft=
ware)">DAP</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretl" title=3D"Gr=
etl">gretl</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R_(programming_lan=
guage)" title=3D"R (programming language)">R</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Python_(programming_language)" title=3D"Python (programming=
 language)">Python</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PSPP" titl=
e=3D"PSPP">PSPP</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolfram_Mathe=
matica" title=3D"Wolfram Mathematica">Wolfram Mathematica</a>, <a href=3D"h=
